<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Katy Cresner Events</title>
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/meyer-reset/2.0/reset.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/bootstrap-css/bootstrap-grid.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Rozha+One" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,400,600,700" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header-background-img">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="logo"></div>
      <nav>
        <ul class="navigation">
          <li><a href="#"> Services. <br><small> What can we do for you</small><hr></a></li>
          <li><a href="#"> Gallery. <br><small> Images of the perfect day</small><hr></a></li>
          <li><a href="#"> Testimonials. <br> <small> What people are saying</small><hr></a></li>
          <li> <a href="#"> Contact. <br> <small> Get in touch</small><hr></a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-11 col-xs-10 header-title">
        <h1>Creating truly <br>
          memorable experiences</h1>
        <p> If there’s one thing we’re passionate about, it’s perfectly planned spectacular events </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="header-social-links">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#">Facebook</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Twitter</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Instagram</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="scroll-for-more">
        <p>Scroll to continue</p>
        <div class="line"></div>
        <div class="dot"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

    <!-- Three step stuff -->

    <div class="row color-block">

      <div class="col-md-4 offset-md-1  first-block-copy">
        <h2>What we do</h2>
        <p>The first thing we do when helping you plan your celebration is get to know you. It’s vitally important that we understand your personality, your likes and dislikes, your style and taste. We listen closely to what you have in mind. It’s your moment, and if we have one aim, it’s to exceed your expectations, making it an occasion that will live long in the memory of everyone who was there.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-1">
        <div class="first-block-img"></div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="row div-margin-top">
        <h2>Designing the perfect day.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="row designing-content">

      <div class="col-md-4">
        <h3>First steps</h3>
        <p> An initial chat allows us to get to know you, gain a full understanding of your requirements and tell you about the many ways in which we can help. This initial consultation is, of course, free of charge and you are under absolutely no obligation to make further use of our services.

          Our primary objective is to alleviate the stress associated with planning and holding an event.</p>
      </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <h3> How can we help? </h3>
          <p> With years of experience behind us and and great working relationships with a host of leading caterers, entertainers, producers, florists, photographers, videographers and venues, we offer the most comprehensive service available.

            From initial planning to the big day itself, we can arrange and oversee every detail, doing our utmost to ensure that everything runs seamlessly and leaving you free to enjoy yourself. </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <h3>  On the day. </h3>
            <p> This is where all those months of planning come together. We’re there to ensure that every last detail is taken care of, from arranging easy access for suppliers to straightening that buttonhole or arranging last minute pressing of a creased shirt. Our reputation, of which we’re extremely proud, stands or falls on our ability to help you to enjoy an absolutely extraordinary day.</p>
        </div>

        </div>

        <!-- carousel -->

        <section class="carousel-container">
          <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-12">
                <button class="next"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
                <button class="prev"><i class="fa fa-arrow-left" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
                <button class="next"><i class="fa fa-arrow-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>
                <button class="prev"><i class="fa fa-arrow-left" aria-hidden="true"></i></button>

                <div class="carousel-inner-container">
                  <div style="display: inline-block;" class="carousel-img">
                    <div class="one">
                      <img src="https://placeimg.com/558/410/people" id="img-1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="two">
                      <img src="https://placeimg.com/400/200/people" id="img-2">
                      <img src="https://placeimg.com/400/200/people" id="img-3">
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="carousel-img">
                    <div class="one">
                      <img src="https://placeimg.com/558/410/animals" id="img-4">
                    </div>
                    <div class="two">
                      <img src="https://placeimg.com/400/200/animals" id="img-5">
                      <img src="https://placeimg.com/400/200/animals" id="img-6">
                    </div>
                  </div>

                </div>

                <div class="pink-box">
                </div>

              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- contact form -->
        <form class="contact-form" method="POST" action="/">
          <h3 class="contact-form-heading">Get in touch</h3>
          {{msg}}

          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-3 offset-2">
              <label for="full-name">Full Name</label>
              <br>
              <input id="full-name-input" type="text" name="name" placeholder="Full name">
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 offset-2">
              <label for="type-of-event">Type of Event</label>
              <br>
              <select id="event-type" name="typeofevent">
                <option value="" disabled selected>Type of event</option>
                <option value="wedding">Wedding</option>
                <option value="bar-mitzvah">Bar Mitzvah</option>
                <option value="bat-mitzvah">Bat Mitzvah</option>
                <option value="Other">Other</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="row form-row">
            <div class="col-3 offset-2">
              <label for="date">Date of event </label>
              <br>
              <input id="date" type="date" name="date">
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 offset-2">
              <label for="email">E-mail</label>
              <br>
              <input id="email" type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter an email address">
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row form-row">
            <div class="col-3 offset-2">
              <label for="phonenumber">Phone number</label>
              <br>
              <input id="phone-number" type="text" name="phonenumber" placeholder="Enter your phone number">
            </div>
            <div class="col-3 offset-2">
              <label for="otherinfo">Other Info</label>
              <textarea id="other-info" name="otherinfo" rows="8" cols="80" placeholder="Enter any other information here"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="row form-row">
            <div class="col-2 offset-5">
              <button class="submit-button" type="submit" name="button">Submit details</button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>

        <footer>

        </footer>
      </body>
      <script src="/js/client.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
      </html>
